text: Phinaea is a genus of plant in family Gesneriaceae. It contains the following species (but this list may be incomplete): * Phinaea albolineata * Phinaea divaricata (syn. Phinaea ecuadorana Wiehler) * Phinaea multiflora ==External links== * World Checklist of Gesneriaceae * Phinaea from The Genera of Gesneriaceae Category:Gesneriaceae Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Gesneriaceae genera
